Getting Started

User, I’d like to introduce you to the COG Design System. COG Design System, I’d like to introduce you to user.

Conventions

Whether you are a developer or designer, if you are going to be coding along-side this design system - please start by learning more about our guidelines.

Webmasters and Designers

You will likely be using this documentation as a resource for how to keep styles consistent and how to implement specific components.Your attention should be directed to the styles, components, and page templates sections!

Developers

You will mostly be maintaining and adding to the above mentioned sections, but you’ll want to pay particular attention to the components, and page templates sections.
